Normal Flow: User completes payment normally

	User clicks â€œPay â‚¹500â€ â†’ backend creates order â†’ frontend gets order_id

	Razorpay Checkout opens â†’ user enters payment info â†’ payment succeeds

	Razorpay returns payment_id + signature to frontend

